The '''Chaos Golem''' is one of the [[Golem (Ruins of Camdozaal)|golems]] found in the [[Ruins of Camdozaal]]. It can be found by awakening the Rubble lying in the far south-east section of Camdozaal, south of the [[body golem]]s. 

When you walk far away from an awakened golem without killing it, it will disintegrate as if it died, without dropping any loot.

Chaos golems are notable for dropping the [[barronite guard]], needed for construction of the [[barronite mace]], and for dropping [[chaos core]]s, used in training [[Runecraft]].

